// graphify MCP launcher snippet — merge into your project's `.mcp.json`
// under "mcpServers" (strip these `//` comments — JSON disallows them).
//
// Canonical launcher: the upstream `graphify-mcp` console script (shipped in
// graphifyy >= 0.8.36; MCP extra `graphifyy[mcp]`). Pin `graphifyy >= 0.8.42`.
// This matches `.claude-plugin/plugin.json` -> mcpServers.graphify.
//
// Prerequisites:
//   1. uv tool install 'graphifyy[mcp]'   (>= 0.8.42)
//   2. graphify .                          (produces graphify-out/graph.json — the server reads it)
//
// graphify MCP is OPTIONAL (enabled.yaml -> mcp-graphify.enabled: false). The
// `/graphify` skill stays the primary path; the MCP adds a live-query layer.
{
  "graphify": {
    "command": "uvx",
    "args": ["graphify-mcp", "serve", "graphify-out/graph.json"]
  }
}
